Gen Signal " optimistic " on meeting 97 view . General Signal Corp said Wednesday it remains optimistic that earnings will be consistent with Wall Street expectations this year . Analayst forecast the company will report $ 0 . 71 per share for Q2 , $ 0 . 81 per share for Q3 , $ 0 . 95 per share for Q4 and $ 2 . 93 for the year , according to First Call . The company said it has " taken actions to improve our operating results . " Also Wednesday , General Signal reported earnings of $ 0 . 47 per share , down from $ 0 . 51 per share reported in Q1 1996 . 
